personal.title: Software Engineer
personal.about_me: Detail-oriented Software Engineer with 4+ years of experience developing and maintaining scalable web applications. Skilled in modern programming languages, cloud platforms, and Agile methodologies. Strong collaborator with a track record of delivering high-quality software on time and within scope. Passionate about building user-friendly solutions and continuously learning emerging technologies such as artificial intelligence, machine learning, and cloud-native applications.

projects.name: React Native Focus Pals
projects.description: Developed Focus Pals, a gamified React Native app that boosts productivity by rewarding focused study sessions with virtual pets and gold, featuring a Deep Focus Mode to prevent distractions. Utilized Firebase for backend services including authentication and data storage.

projects.name: Battleship Game
projects.description: Developed a Battleship game implementing Test Driven Development to enable turn-based gameplay with ship management, gameboard functionality, and player interaction through a user interface. It supports real and computer players with attack tracking and game state management.

projects.name: React Memory Card
projects.description: Developed a React-based Memory Card game that challenges users to click unique cards without repetition, featuring a scoreboard and dynamic card shuffling with images fetched from the Pokemon API.
